description:
In this episode, we uncover Jesus' important experience at the Temple. The Bible records little about Jesus' childhood and adolescent years, except for this one instance where he visits the temple in Jerusalem with his parents. It was here that at the age of 12, Jesus understood his divine mission from God. This story has powerful and important lessons for us today.
